<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-346] remove the kill command fro mthe client port.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-346</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;we should just remove the kill command from the client port. Its a security risk (though we do not have much security right now) to be able to kill the server from a tcp port without any authentication... &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
